  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0ba3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 ; \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 14 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sexual harassment of female police in Batticaloa; Police officer remanded for 14 days",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today Thursday (07) the Batticaloa Magistrate Court Judge Peter Paul ordered that the police driver who sexually harassed a female police officer on duty at the Kokuvil Police Station in Batticaloa be remanded for 14 days until the 20th.",
        "On the day of the incident, Wednesday afternoon, the female police officer working as a female police officer in the women's section of the said police station has appealed to the officer in charge of the police station, alleging that the police officer who was working there as a driver held her hand and sexually harassed her at the police station.",
        "After bringing this to the attention of the Senior Superintendent of Police, the officer in charge of the police station immediately suspended the said police officer from duty and after the Sires Superintendent of Police advised him to arrest him and produce him in court, the said police officer was arrested.",
        "The arrested person is a 35-year-old from Amparai who is working as a police driver. He was produced before the Batticaloa Magistrate's Court on Thursday (07)."
      ],
